00:00:03.300 --> 00:00:08.760
Guido von Rossum, who created and has been shepherding the language for the last 30 years,

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:12.200
has stepped down from decision-making around the Python language.

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:17.900
Join Carol Willing and Brett Cannon, both longtime core developers and Python leaders,

00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:23.500
along with my co-host at Python Bytes, Brian Okken, as we discuss what the future holds for

00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:27.020
Python and how this change will affect how Python is created and how it evolves.

