I think looking at it, I don't know that there's ever an easy way to change how you make decisions and governance when you have many personalities involved.

00:15:08.780 --> 00:15:11.740
And it's unfortunate how it came out.

00:15:11.740 --> 00:15:24.800
But I think there had to be something that would give us a catalyst in the developer community to really take some of these issues on that are not necessarily new issues to us.

